        <p>The <a href="https://www.w3.org/community/dpvcg/">W3C Data Privacy Vocabularies and Controls Community Group (DPVCG)</a> works on the mission to develop a taxonomy of privacy terms, which include in particular terms from the new European General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR), such as a taxonomy of personal data as well as a classification of purposes (i.e., purposes for data collection), and events of disclosures, consent, and processing such personal data.</p>
